description: After some new lunch box ideas? Jazz things up with this healthier chicken wrap recipe. The little ones will love the flavour combo of chicken, black bean and corn.
keywords: Wrap,Seafood free,Blueberry,Tree nut free,Egg free,Healthier Easier,Sesame free,Mandarin,Chicken,Spinach,Peanut free
name: Chicken, black bean & corn wrap lunch boxes Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Bring a medium saucepan of water to the boil over medium heat. Add chicken. Poach for 15 minutes or until cooked through. Drain chicken and cool. Shred chicken and toss with 1/4 cup yoghurt and paprika. Season with pepper.
Top wraps with spinach, beans, corn and chicken mixture. Wrap tightly to enclose filling. Serve wraps in lunch boxes with remaining yoghurt, mandarin and blueberries.
